@startuml 03-self-correction-loop
' === METADATA ===
' id:           03-self-correction-loop
' title:        3A Studio: Self-Correction Loop
' version:      1.1
' status:       current
' created:      2026-06-12
' lastModified: 2026-06-12
' author:       AI Agent
' diagramType:  sequence
' scope:        Self-correction API: generate -> judge -> revise loop with DB persistence
' dependencies: []
